videos.description: Khris Middleton throws a quick alley-oop to Giannis Antetokounmpo who draws the contact and somehow gets the ball to bounce in for an and-1 basket.

videos.headline: Middleton lobs to Giannis for and-1 layup

videos.description: Brook Lopez comes up with the block on one end, then Giannis Antetokounmpo goes coast-to-coast for the and-1 layup finish.

tracking.trackingName: NBA_One-Play (Lopez's block leads to Giannis and-1) 2021/02/03 ESHEET

videos.headline: Lopez's block leads to Giannis and-1

videos.description: Jrue Holiday throws a quick pass back to Giannis Antetokounmpo, who cuts through the lane to drop the hammer on a powerful dunk.

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo has a bit of fun as he experiments with being a sideline photographer as the Bucks blow out the Pacers.

videos.description: Giannis Antetokounmpo explains to Ariel Helwani that he was sneaking pictures of his brother on the sideline during the Bucks' game against the Pacers.
